    "creatureType": "",
    "details": {
      "description": "<p>Coded Thassilonian wall-text (@Check[type:society|dc:30] + the language to decipher) that claims to warn of perils — and self-alters so it can never be finished. Ancient Shoanti skeletons (their gear: <strong>+1 hide armor, a +1 striking frost earth breaker, a +1 striking returning totem spear</strong>) died of thirst mid-sentence here.</p>",
      "disable": "<p>@Check[type:thievery|dc:33] to deface a keystone glyph, or <em>dispel magic</em> (5th rank). Only readers who comprehend <strong>Thassilonian</strong> can be affected at all.</p>",
